      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay thanks. i've heard about that Reye's thing but i'm just worried because he's really miserable and the ibuprofen we have is for adults so i don't know if the dose will be right. is aspirin really that risky for an 8 year old? i mean it's just one dose to help him sleep",
